{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4b2746d029","title":"目前阶段陈乘谭军与刘邓军只作战略配合","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a0d0176bc7","index":0,"year":1947,"month":6,"day":1,"articleId":"4b2746d029"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji23","name":"毛泽东全集第23卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji23.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji23":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d5761b81f9","type":"paragraph","text":"目前阶段陈乘谭军与刘邓军","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"4b2746d029"},{"id":"29a87833f4","type":"paragraph","text":"只作战略配合口","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"4b2746d029"},{"id":"f75d3fe6a4","type":"paragraph","text":"（1947年6月1日）陈、菜、谭，并告刘、世电”器。（一）无论刘邓是否按原定时间行动，你们和刘邓之间在目前阶段上均只须作战略配合，不须作战役配合。你们的战役作战应完全单独进行。（二）在情况许可（即确有胜利把握）条件下，我们希望你们于六月上句及下句各有一次战役作战","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"4b2746d029"},{"id":"e8d9891a04","type":"paragraph","text":"军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"4b2746d029"},{"id":"d88df8d203","type":"paragraph","text":"东未[1]这是毛泽东为中共中央军委起草的给华东野战军司令员兼政治委员陈毅、副司令质栗裕和副政治委员源震林的电报。[2]政治委员。[3]指1947年5月31日陈叙、栗裕、谭震林给中共中央和刘伯承、邓小平的电报。电报询问刘邓大军是否按原计划出击，以便布置配合作战。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"4b2746d029"}],"page":{"id":"8349e53f41","publicationId":"maoquanji23","articleId":"4b2746d029","start":76,"end":76}}}},"__N_SSG":true}